        <h3 class="struggle__card-title">Balancing Physical and Mental Health</h3>
        <p class="struggle__card-text">Like a chess game, Brazilian Jiu Jitsu requires a high level of concentration, while engaged in a fun, calorie burning, experience that results in a mental release.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 — Self-Defense -->
      <div class="struggle__card reveal">
        <div class="struggle__card-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
